_sName: Bugga's Shitty Map a Day Map Pack
_sText:
I just got surprised by a screamer so I haven't slept, so sorry if this writing is worse than the usual. I made these maps in a day each just for fun. I had help from people such as wunderjam (who made the first level of bhop_r3turndaslab) and madman (who got runs for me to showcase the map). I made these maps for fun and stuff.

MAPS THE PACK INCLUDES
-bhop_r3turndaslab
-bhop_wifiscifi
-bhop_explordus
-bhop_kz_creation
